title: Amber Tamblyn Shares a Hilarious Postnursing Fashion Fail That All Moms Can Relate To
text:
A post shared by Amber Tamblyn (@amberrosetamblyn) on Mar 4, 2017 at 7:15am PST 
You may remember her from The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants , but Amber Tamblyn's all grown up now and providing us with the relatable parenting humor we need. After welcoming her first child with husband David Cross , Amber is learning that breastfeeding can leave some interesting spots on clothing. Ah, the marks of motherhood! 
The new mommy took to Instagram to flaunt some chic postnursing stains, and we can't help but applaud her mommy humor. "Who Wore It Better?" she captioned the photo above. "Left tit or right tit? #MilkLife #StarsTheyreJustLikeUs!" 
We're going to assume that this breastfeeding tee will not be arriving in Blake Lively's mailbox in the same fashion that magic pair of vintage jeans once did.
